Merge pull request #106 from EvanDotPro/hotfix/module-php Revert PR #91, move Module.php out of src/

Revert PR #91, move Module.php out of src/ This was mainly to appease composer's PSR0 autoloader, however we should
not have to alter module structure (especially the one and only single
requirement for a ZF2 module) simply for the sake of composer. Besides,
composer supports classmaps which resolves the issue just fine.
Changed form buttons to button element.
Utilize ZfcBase ProvidesEventsInputFilter Triggers init event in login/register input filters. Resolves issue #74.
ClassMethod hydrator default changed
Do not use getElements() to loop over form elements It does not respect priorities.

Base user form should not trigger init event This makes it so that extending forms (registration, eventually user
editing, etc) that have their own constructor and modify the form make
it impossible for listeners to the init event to override what they've
done to the form.
